---
title: Cal Smart Tzatziki-Feta Turkey Burgers with Fresh Garden Salad
description: Turkey patties get a fresh and zesty lift from lemons and sliced cucumbers while the feta-boosted tzatziki schmeared over top injects these burgers with briny goodness. A fresh side salad lightens things up for a light summer supper!
